headline: FLOWERS FOODS ELECTS STERLING A. SPAINHOUR TO BOARD OF DIRECTORS
summary: Flowers Foods, Inc. (NYSE: FLO) today announced that its board of directors has elected a new board member. Sterling A. Spainhour, executive vice president and chief legal officer of Southern Company will join Flowers Foods' board of directors effective Oct. 1, 2025. He will serve on the audit committee and finance committee of the board.

headline: Things to Weigh Before Choosing Between OKLO and SO Stock
summary: SO delivers steady dividends and proven nuclear execution, while OKLO offers high-risk growth tied to small modular reactors.
